            <div class="slides">
              <div class="item">
                <div class="wrapper">
                  <div class="stars svg"></div>  
                  <div class="phrase">"King’s Crest was crucial in all the elements to start up. They coached me in terms of why I started my business. It’s more important to know the why, and what you’re offering people, versus how you’re doing it. You have to find the strong why. That was really crucial."</div>
