                  <div class="stars svg"></div>  
                  <div class="phrase">"Saul is a bulldog! That’s a compliment in every sense of the word. If you need something to get done, Saul will get it done. He’s the kind of person you can hand any project to, big or small, and know that he will get it done with excellence no matter what obstacles he has in his way. He’s smart, organized, focused, driven, and is a rare person who can work in startups and Fortune 500 companies with equal effectiveness. I highly recommend Saul and envy anyone who hires him."</div>
